        {
            "title": "拉加德:即使通膨上升\"非持續性\" 歐洲央行仍可能調整政策",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yztcdWicAvWjMjT_21H1Rg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_5_M_1440048359.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 歐洲央行總裁<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"拉加德\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:拉加德;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/拉加德\">拉加德</a>表示,伊朗戰爭導致的通膨偏離歐洲央行2%目標若\"非持續性\",可能引發一些溫和的政策緊縮措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拉加德在德國一場活動上表示,\"大規模且持續性\"的偏離需要\"有力的貨幣政策行動\",以防止這些變化在較長時期內根深蒂固。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"我們不會因猶豫而癱瘓:我們致力於在中期內實現2%通膨目標的承諾是無條件的,\"拉加德說。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-746c1a44-8d75-32b3-92a5-e1580baef691-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這番言論發表之際,伊朗戰爭引發的能源衝擊威脅重新點燃歐元區的通膨壓力,而此前市場認為通膨已幾乎得到控制。卡塔爾能源基礎設施遭受的攻擊尤其推高了歐洲天然氣價格,歐洲高度依賴這個波斯灣國家的天然氣進口。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,伊朗戰爭導致霍爾木茲海峽關閉,這條位於伊朗南部的重要水道承載著全球五分之一的石油運輸。自2月底衝突爆發以來,油價大幅飆升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">面對這些新的壓力,歐洲央行在上週的政策會議上維持利率不變。但央行上調了今年的通膨預期,顯示官員們對未來幾個月價格加速上漲保持警惕。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週稍早針對歐元區商業活動的一項調查也警告\"滯脹警鐘響起\",指的是頑固通膨和增長停滯並存的經濟趨勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"如果當前衝擊僅限於能源市場,可能對整體通膨影響有限。但如果衝擊加劇或持續,傳導效應可能加速,\"拉加德警告。她補充說,如果衝擊導致\"大幅但非持續性地超出我們的目標\",一些\"有節制的政策調整可能是適當的\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%89%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B7-%E5%8D%B3%E4%BD%BF%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E9%9D%9E%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%80%A7-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96-104630365.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 18:51:45",
