        {
            "title": "首匯原價加推25伙｜折實均呎2.15萬維持不變｜本周六發售123伙 暫超額認購逾17倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒基地產旗下紅磡大型重建項目MIDTOWN SOUTH第5期首匯，昨日（24日）公布第3號價單，加推25伙，涵蓋一至兩房。新一批單位折實均呎為21,498元，與上周日（22日）公布的第2號價單相同；若與上周五（20日）首張價單的折實均呎20,988元相比，則高約2.43%，整體定價水平相若，屬原價加推。另外，是次價單折實入場費由548.8萬元起。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發展商將於本周六（28日）以價單形式發售123伙，另有8伙以招標形式推出。截至今日（25日），項目累收約2,220個認購登記，以首輪發售123伙計，超額認購逾17倍。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7db0961f-38da-350b-9dd8-1e8c5463b55d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"首匯價單\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:首匯價單;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4swg0e9\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">首匯價單</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【3月新盤懶人包】港九新界全新供應！ 康城最後一期即將應市 短樓花樓盤登場｜瑜意、瑧玥、首匯、薈淳擬推售｜港島南岸、海瑅灣I及牛池灣項目陸續登場\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【3月新盤懶人包】港九新界全新供應！ 康城最後一期即將應市 短樓花樓盤登場｜瑜意、瑧玥、首匯、薈淳擬推售｜港島南岸、海瑅灣I及牛池灣項目陸續登場;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4sqtdVI\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【3月新盤懶人包】港九新界全新供應！ 康城最後一期即將應市 短樓花樓盤登場｜瑜意、瑧玥、首匯、薈淳擬推售｜港島南岸、海瑅灣I及牛池灣項目陸續登場</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>主打一房  折實均呎約2.15萬</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發展商公布第3號價單，共加推25伙。新一批單位實用面積介乎265至347平方呎，涵蓋19伙一房及6伙兩房，主打一房戶型。按定價計算，整批單位市值約1.7億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">售價方面，新價單定價由609.8萬至771.3萬元，實用呎價介乎21,787至26,695元。扣除最高10%折扣優惠後，折實售價約548.8萬至694.2萬元，折實呎價約19,608至24,026元，折實均呎為21,498元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">定價走勢方面，是次加推單位的折實均呎與上周日（22日）公布第2號價單相同，均為21,498元。雖然兩批價單沒有同柱單位對比呎價，但整體定價水平相若，屬於原價加推。不過，若與上周五（20日）公布的首張價單折實均呎為20,988元相比，這批單位則高出約2.43%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>一房入場費約549萬元 兩房約680萬元起</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">綜觀三號價單各戶型，一房入場單位為19樓H室，實用面積265平方呎，折實售價約548.8萬元，折實呎價約20,710元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Edyrn6zZo3WwPGHMu0W0uA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/311f7ed957c5e9135e56fdfbb0e158ba\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩房入場單位為12樓J室，實用面積347平方呎，折實售價約680.4萬元。該單位同時為今批折實呎價最低的單位，折實呎價約19,608元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DcpVkn3vEyRbmEkuIVXzEQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/5a3f687704a89bc9ecd21b7aa890c5af\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於今批折實呎價最高的單位，為28樓F室一房戶，實用面積266平方呎，折實售價約639.09萬元，折實呎價約24,026元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>項目背景</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首匯位於紅磡黃埔街8號，由恒基兆業發展。項目設有1座住宅大樓，共提供241伙單位，實用面積由228至850平方呎，戶型涵蓋一至四房。交通方面，由項目步行至港鐵何文田站約需7分鐘。校網方面，小學屬35校網，中學屬九龍城區。項目預計關鍵日期為2026年12月31日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"薈淳\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:薈淳;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/薈淳\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">薈淳</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"首匯\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:首匯;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/首匯\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">首匯</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"瑧玥\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:瑧玥;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/瑧玥\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">瑧玥</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"瑜意\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:瑜意;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/瑜意\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">瑜意</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"港島南岸\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:港島南岸;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/港島南岸-27919\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">港島南岸</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"九龍城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:九龍城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/九龍城-27371\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">九龍城</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"何文田\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:何文田;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/何文田-27373\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">何文田</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"牛池灣\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:牛池灣;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/牛池灣-27395\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">牛池灣</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"康城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:康城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/康城-27482\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">康城</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\